{"tid":826863,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 遊泰注意 ] 泰國登革熱致69人死亡 首都曼谷成為災區","createTime":"2018-09-18T14:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T16:12:28.000Z","uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6e4fd589cb488aa5cfe7e45352db57f10d61b4e8","tid":826863,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T14:01:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2018/09/20180918_thailand_dengue_fever_1_fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2018%2F09%2F20180918_thailand_dengue_fever_1_fb.jpg&h=df0e6c20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰國今年登革熱疫情嚴重，截至本月上旬，已爆發5萬多宗登革熱病例，其中有69人死亡。首都曼谷更成為重災區，已有近5900宗病例，當中5人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n曼谷市長萬孟周一(9月17日)說，泰國目前處於雨季，曼谷近日持續降雨，污水積聚，導致花斑蚊滋生，曼谷多個區暴發登革熱疫情。目前衛生部門正密切跟蹤各區疫情，在疫區噴藥滅蚊，並定期調查患者所在的辦公點、學校、住宅區等地的衛生情況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2018/09/20180918_thailand_dengue_fever_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2018%2F09%2F20180918_thailand_dengue_fever_1.jpg&h=0fe39b1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曼谷市衛生廳最新數據顯示，今年1月至9月8日，泰國全國已發現52670宗登革熱病例，當中69人死亡。曼谷則發現了5899宗登革熱病例。<br />\n<br />\n曼谷市長提醒民眾，若發現有發燒3日不退的症狀，須及時就醫。若發現登革熱患者須及時匯報，以防止疫情擴散。政府建議居民勤加打掃家居、避免積水，為蓄水容器蓋上蓋子以防止蚊子滋生，並配合衛生防疫人員進行衛生檢查及滅蚊行動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2018/09/20180918_thailand_dengue_fever_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2018%2F09%2F20180918_thailand_dengue_fever_2.jpg&h=816c9cfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">登革熱是一種由蚊子傳播的急性病毒性傳染病，其典型症狀是<ins>發燒、頭痛和關節痛</ins>等。登革熱分為普通登革熱和出血登革熱，後者死亡率較高。目前為止，登革熱尚無特效的治療藥物。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"63195c0b635dcf7d90f4aec6a5218faf54de9056","tid":826863,"uid":26467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:07:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dfb733387e4e923c5cec30b06bf9f7664161279","tid":826863,"uid":31261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:11:14.000Z","msg":"泰多蚊"},{"pid":"bcf5f00fe1af13aab5f1bdb1d72b8ee315e98541","tid":826863,"uid":106426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:12:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}